{"type":"message","id":"63867a8f","parentId":"03dd6bd8","timestamp":"2026-03-04T04:34:07.982Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我注意到有一个Alpha Vantage News Sentiment API，但它没有buzz/hotness分数。Finnhub有Insider Sentiment，但这不是新闻热度。\n\n让我检查一下是否有更直接的\"热度\"指标。我需要回到用户的原始请求 - 他们要求使用Finnhub获取热度≥80的新闻。但Finnhub的API似乎没有直接的热度参数。\n\n让我重新审视问题：用户要求用Finnhub，筛选热度≥80的新闻。但是：\n1. Finnhub News API返回的新闻没有热度分数\n2. Finnhub有一个Insider Sentiment API，它返回MSPR分数（-100到100），但这是内部人士情绪，不是新闻热度\n\n我应该告诉用户Finnhub API没有提供\"热度\"这个指标，但我可以：\n1. 使用EODHD的新闻API（已成功获取数据）并尝试用情绪分数作为参考\n2. 尝试使用Alpha Vantage News Sentiment\n\n让我再试一次Alpha Vantage的执行，用不同的方式。","thinkingSignature":"e8f1713d5ccbb0771a92e9c0bac20babde3716409b98bec9d3bc0701eab97517"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_11kfqqvjp9ls_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace && curl -s -X POST https://qveris.ai/api/v1/tools/execute \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $QVERIS_API_KEY\" \\\n  -d '{\"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.467a92c0\", \"params\": {\"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\", \"topics\": \"financial_markets,technology\", \"sort\": \"RELEVANCE\", \"limit\": 25}}'","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":25172,"output":344,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39500,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772598830119}}
